00:00:11.364 --> 00:00:14.336
to think about the area between curves.

00:00:14.336 --> 00:00:16.124
So let's say we care about the region

00:00:16.124 --> 00:00:19.583
from x equals a to x equals b

00:00:19.583 --> 00:00:23.229
between y equals f of x
and y is equal to g of x.

00:00:23.229 --> 00:00:25.063
So that would be

00:00:25.063 --> 00:00:26.313
this area right

00:00:27.803 --> 00:00:28.636
over here.

